This is a basic web calculator that performs the four fundamental arithmetic operations: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, and Division.

It displays two numbers on the screen and provides a user-friendly interface with buttons for better visual interaction.

 Features
- 📐 Clean UI with responsive layout
- ➕ Addition
- ➖ Subtraction
- ✖️ Multiplication
- ➗ Division
- 🧮 Results displayed instantly

Technologies Used
- HTML – Structure of the calculator
- CSS – Styling and layout using Grid
- JavaScript** – Logic for operations and dynamic DOM manipulation
